metadata.title: Black Box CAT6 Modular Plug - Unshielded, RJ45, 8-Wire, 50-Pack
features: Eight-conductor plug is designed for high-speed applications.
For 24 or 26 AWG solid or stranded cable with a diameter from -0.197-in. (5 mm) up to 0.354" (9 mm).
Use a conductor load bar (included) for ease of termination and to keep the integrity of the twisted pairs.
description: 8-conductor plug designed for high-speed applications. For 24 or 26AWG solid or stranded cable w/ diameter from -0.197-in. up to 0.354". Conductive NEXT Reduction system. Comply with FCC requirements. Meets/exceeds CAT6 specs.
